            (31, 'trc-train-number', 'TRC Train Number', NULL, '<div class=\"product-tabs-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-12 poduct-tabs-inner\">\r\n<div class=\"woocommerce-tabs wc-tabs-wrapper tabs-layout-tabs\">\r\n<div class=\"woodmart-tab-wrapper\">\r\n<div id=\"tab-description\" class=\"woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--description panel entry-content wc-tab\">\r\n<div class=\"wc-tab-inner \r\n										\">\r\n<div class=\"\">\r\n<h2>DESCRIPTION</h2>\r\n<p>32396 &ndash; Product Description<br />It is a wooden train consisting of several 11 small pieces, which are a series of train numbered from 0 to 9</p>\r\n<p>:Suitable age<br />Two years or more</p>\r\n<p>:acquired skills<br />Strengthening fine motor skills in terms of eye-hand consistency, which increases motor intelligence-</p>\r\n<p>Developing motor intelligence skills by moving and installing the numbered train parts and arranging them correctly.-</p>\r\n<p>Developing the skills of sport, logical intelligence through learning the basics of mathematics (by arranging numbers)-</p>\r\n<p>Developing visual (spatial) intelligence skills by knowing the correct location of the numbered piece-</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"woodmart-tab-wrapper\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"woodmart-tab-wrapper\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"container related-and-upsells\">\r\n<div class=\"related-products\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', NULL, NULL, 'en', 35, '2021-12-01 18:57:24', '2021-12-01 18:57:24'),
            (32, 'rkm-ktar-trc', 'رقم قطار TRC', NULL, '<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>الوصف</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><br />32396 - وصف المنتج<br />إنه قطار خشبي يتكون من عدة 11 قطعة صغيرة ، وهي عبارة عن سلسلة قطارات مرقمة من 0 إلى 9</p>\r\n<p>: العمر المناسب<br />سنتان أو أكثر</p>\r\n<p>:المهارات المكتسبة<br />تقوية المهارات الحركية الدقيقة من حيث تناسق العين واليد ، مما يزيد من الذكاء الحركي-</p>\r\n<p>تنمية مهارات الذكاء الحركي عن طريق تحريك وتركيب قطع القطار المرقمة وترتيبها بشكل صحيح. -</p>\r\n<p>تنمية المهارات الرياضية والذكاء المنطقي من خلال تعلم أساسيات الرياضيات (بترتيب الأرقام) -</p>\r\n<p>تنمية مهارات الذكاء البصري (المكاني) من خلال معرفة الموقع الصحيح للقطعة المرقمة-</p>', NULL, NULL, 'ar', 35, '2021-12-01 18:57:24', '2021-12-01 18:57:24'),
            (33, 'trc-puzzle-placing-colored-balls-with-stick', 'TRC Puzzle Placing Colored Balls With Stick', NULL, '<div class=\"product-tabs-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-12 poduct-tabs-inner\">\r\n<div class=\"woocommerce-tabs wc-tabs-wrapper tabs-layout-tabs\">\r\n<div class=\"woodmart-tab-wrapper\">\r\n<div id=\"tab-description\" class=\"woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--description panel entry-content wc-tab\">\r\n<div class=\"wc-tab-inner \r\n										\">\r\n<div class=\"\">\r\n<h2>DESCRIPTION</h2>\r\n<p>32397 &ndash; It is a square-shaped board with small holes of different colors (red &ndash; green &ndash; orange &ndash; blue) and different colored balls and a wooden stick, the child uses the Chinese stick to put the colored ball in the right place for it according to the shape of the cards.</p>\r\n<p>Suitable Age:</p>\r\n<p>Three years and older.</p>\r\n<p>acquired skills:</p>\r\n<p>Strengthening fine motor skills by controlling the child&rsquo;s wooden stick and placing the balls in their appropriate place, which increases the child&rsquo;s motor intelligence.</p>\r\n<p>&ndash; Developing visual intelligence skills (spatial) through the ability to place colored balls in the appropriate place for them on the wooden board.</p>\r\n<p>&ndash; Developing personal intelligence skills by strengthening focus and developing the child&rsquo;s mental abilities.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"woodmart-tab-wrapper\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"woodmart-tab-wrapper\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"container related-and-upsells\">\r\n<div class=\"related-products\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', NULL, NULL, 'en', 34, '2021-12-01 19:00:00', '2021-12-01 19:00:00'),
            (34, 'lghz-trc-odaa-alkrat-almlon-balaasa', 'لغز TRC وضع الكرات الملونة بالعصا', NULL, '<p><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>الوصف</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><br />32397 - هو لوح مربع الشكل به فتحات صغيرة بألوان مختلفة (أحمر - أخضر - برتقالي - أزرق) وكرات ملونة مختلفة وعصا خشبية ، يستخدم الطفل العصا الصينية لوضع الكرة الملونة في المكان المناسب لها حسب شكل البطاقات.</p>\r\n<p>العمر المناسب:</p>\r\n<p>ثلاث سنوات وما فوق.</p>\r\n<p>المهارات المكتسبة:</p>\r\n<p>تقوية المهارات الحركية الدقيقة من خلال التحكم في عصا الطفل الخشبية ووضع الكرات في مكانها المناسب مما يزيد من ذكاء الطفل الحركي.</p>\r\n<p>- تنمية مهارات الذكاء البصري (المكاني) من خلال القدرة على وضع الكرات الملونة في المكان المناسب لها على السبورة الخشبية.</p>\r\n<p>- تنمية مهارات الذكاء الشخصي من خلال تقوية التركيز وتنمية القدرات العقلية للطفل.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'ar', 34, '2021-12-01 19:00:00', '2021-12-01 19:00:00'),
            (35, 'trc-the-phone-game', 'TRC The Phone Game', NULL, '<div class=\"product-tabs-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-12 poduct-tabs-inner\">\r\n<div class=\"woocommerce-tabs wc-tabs-wrapper tabs-layout-tabs\">\r\n<div class=\"woodmart-tab-wrapper\">\r\n<div id=\"tab-description\" class=\"woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--description panel entry-content wc-tab\">\r\n<div class=\"wc-tab-inner \r\n										\">\r\n<div class=\"\">\r\n<h2>DESCRIPTION</h2>\r\n<p>32398 &ndash; Product Description:</p>\r\n<p>It is a game that is a multi-use phone shape (cutting shapes &ndash; numbers &ndash; a car). The child uses the phone to talk or move the car using the rope in the game or install the pieces of shapes in the right place.</p>\r\n<p>Suitable Age:</p>\r\n<p>From 6 months and older.</p>\r\n<p>acquired skills:</p>\r\n<p>&ndash; Developing academic intelligence skills through the child&rsquo;s ability to learn some different geometric shapes or numbers using the game in front of him, which increases his academic intelligence.</p>\r\n<p>&ndash; Developing the skills of motor intelligence (physical) through the child&rsquo;s ability to control the engineering pieces in the game and put them in the right place.</p>\r\n<p>&ndash; Developing the skills of visual intelligence (spatial) through the child&rsquo;s ability to place the geometric pieces in their correct places.</p>\r\n<p>&ndash; Developing personal intelligence skills through the child&rsquo;s ability to increase awareness and focus, which increases the child&rsquo;s mental capabilities.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"woodmart-tab-wrapper\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"woodmart-tab-wrapper\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"container related-and-upsells\">\r\n<div class=\"related-products\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', NULL, NULL, 'en', 33, '2021-12-01 19:02:31', '2021-12-01 19